reviewText:
A masterful show of musical talent through two long and intertwined careers. Two towering figures of people's music in the world today at their best, distilled to the essence without need or interference of any other instruments but theirs.
No need to go into an analysis song by song: its uniformly priceless. Don't miss it if you know them, and if you are not familiar with Brazilian music and have good taste there's no better place to start

I was hoping for a more up-beat show since they ate my favorite Brazilian artist and I have watched many of their live concerts, shich are normally up-beat!! This is beautiful though :-) I love them!!!
